-- IN with a set subquery on the right is cacheable without the opt-in
-- hits: 1
-- scalar subquery in the LEFT operand of IN is gated (not cached without the opt-in)
-- hits: 0
-- with the opt-in, the same query is cacheable
-- hits: 1
-- the opt-in setting is part of the cache key: =1 entry is not reused under =0
-- hits with opt-in (warm): 1
-- hits without opt-in (must be 0): 0
